---
import Layout from "../components/Layout.astro";
---
<Layout title="Sign in" hideSidebar={true}>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">Account</div>
    <h1>Sign in</h1>
    <p class="lede">The catalog is fully public — there's nothing to sign in to (yet).</p>
  </section>
  <div class="surface prose">
    <p>An account flow is planned for v0.5 to let you star favourite packages, get notified on new releases, and sync across devices. For now, every package page is freely accessible.</p>
    <p><a href="/" class="button">Browse packages</a></p>
  </div>
</Layout>
